dback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 19, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bdv1665702674820.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bdv1665702674820.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bdv1665702674820.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bdv1665702674820\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bdv1665702674820___webwidgets__479687\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The [webwidgets] section of the initialization file contains logical widget\n    definitions for fields used in Dynamic Server Page (DSP) components.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bdv1665702674820__topic_d147197e1_d147198e1_d147199e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdv1665702674820__d6344e17\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalWidgetName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PhysicalWidgetName</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">WidgetProperty1</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value1</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">;</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">WidgetProperty2</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value2</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">;</code>...<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bdv1665702674820__topic_d106082e1_d106083e1_d106084e1_d106085e1_d106086e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d322117e99\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdv1665702674820__p_d147206e1_d147207e1_d147208e1\">Each logical widget maps to a physical widget, and optionally sets some of its properties. The property values defined in this section override the hard-coded defaults of the physical widget.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdv1665702674820__p_d147209e1_d147210e1_d147211e1\">The maximum length of the widget property string is 1024 characters.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdv1665702674820__p_d147212e1_d147213e1_d147214e1\">You can use this section to define your own logical\n        widgets for fields.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[webwidgets]\n; Logical to physical widget mapping of field widget for DSPs\nEditBox=htmlinput(html:type=text;detail=dblclick)\nTextArea=htmltextarea(detail=dblclick)\nCommandButton=htmlinput(html:type=button;clientsyntaxcheck=false)[syntax=ned]\nCommandButton_updatable=htmlinput(html:type=button;clientsyntaxcheck=false)\nCheckBox=htmlinput(html:type=checkbox)\nDropDownList=htmlselect(html:size=1)\nListBox=htmlselect(html:size=3)\nDatePicker=htmlinput(html:type=date)\nRadioGroup=htmlradiogroup(style:display=inline-block)\n...\nAttributesOnly=genericHTML\nDspContainer=dspcontainer</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjk1665702557273.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Widgets</a><p>In Uniface, widgets are user interface controls. They can display data values, control how values are modified, and determine the appearance of those objects. Most widgets are field-level widgets.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qxh1718771608803.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Widget Reference: Dynamic Server Pages</a><p>Widgets in dynamic server pages (DSPs) determine the appearance and behavior of fields, labels, occurrences, and entities displayed in the client browser.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525996\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525996\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[webwidgets] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 19, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The [webwidgets] section of the initialization file contains logical widget definitions for fields used in Dynamic Server Page (DSP) components. LogicalWidgetName = PhysicalWidgetName { ( WidgetProperty1 = Value1 ; WidgetProperty2 = Value2 ; ... ) } Description Each logical widget maps to a physical widget, and optionally sets some of its properties. The property values defined in this section override the hard-coded defaults of the physical widget. The maximum length of the widget property string is 1024 characters. You can use this section to define your own logical widgets for fields. [webwidgets] ; Logical to physical widget mapping of field widget for DSPs EditBox=htmlinput(html:type=text;detail=dblclick) TextArea=htmltextarea(detail=dblclick) CommandButton=htmlinput(html:type=button;clientsyntaxcheck=false)[syntax=ned] CommandButton_updatable=htmlinput(html:type=button;clientsyntaxcheck=false) CheckBox=htmlinput(html:type=checkbox) DropDownList=htmlselect(html:size=1) ListBox=htmlselect(html:size=3) DatePicker=htmlinput(html:type=date) RadioGroup=htmlradiogroup(style:display=inline-block) ... AttributesOnly=genericHTML DspContainer=dspcontainer Copy Related Links Widgets In Uniface, widgets are user interface controls. They can display data values, control how values are modified, and determine the appearance of those objects. Most widgets are field-level widgets. Widget Reference: Dynamic Server Pages Widgets in dynamic server pages (DSPs) determine the appearance and behavior of fields, labels, occurrences, and entities displayed in the client browser. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}